# NouvoSmartLife-Policy
Nouvo Smart Life Mobile Application Privacy Policy

1. Introduction

Nouvo Smart Technologies company respects the privacy of the users. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose your information when you use our smart home application.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect the following information from you:

Device Information: Information about the device you use to access the App, such as device model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers.
Usage Data: Information about how you use the App, such as the features you access, the devices you control, and the time you spend using the App.
Account Information: If you create an account with us, we may collect your name and email address.
3. How We Use Your Information

We may use your information to:

Provide and improve the App and its functionalities.
Communicate with you about the App, such as sending you important updates or notifications.
Analyze how you use the App to personalize your experience.
Comply with legal and regulatory requirements.
4. Data Sharing

We may share your information with third-party service providers who help us operate the App. These service providers are contractually obligated to keep your information confidential and secure.

We will not share your information with any third-party for marketing purposes without your consent.

5. Data Security

We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no internet transmission or electronic storage method is completely secure.

6. User Choices

You may have the following choices regarding your information:

Access your information.
Correct your information.
Delete your information.
For more information on how to exercise these choices, please contact us.

7. Children's Privacy

We do not knowingly collect information from children under the age of 3 years old. If you are a parent or guardian and you believe your child has provided us with information, please contact us.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at info@nouvo.ir.
